CatDescriptText: Sign in background reads "Come one! Come all!  To the summer cabaret ball, Fri., Sept. 29, from 12 midnite till ?  Ritz Cabaret, 55 Fullerton Street, given by Century Sporting Club...music by Jimmy Baldwin and his Downbeat Boys, featuring and all-star floor show..."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of two men wearing light colored fedora hats, and two women, posed at bar, with poster in background with Double V Campaign logo and inscribed "Indian Summer Cabaret Ball...Ritz Cabaret..."
